Class Arrival

All Implemented Interfaces:
IEvent, Comparable
public class Arrival
extends AbstractEvent
implements IEvent

Arrival event, i.e registration time of earthquake's wave on the given instrument. Collection of Arrival(s) is a property of a trace and can be found in the it's events list.
